    <item>
      <title>亚洲工厂仍面临混合需求反弹的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/asian-factories-remain-under-pressure-as-demand-rebound-eludes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲工厂活动的主要指标未能扭转 11 月份的悲观情绪，因为全球商品需求依然疲软，而中国经济复苏步履蹒跚，削弱了乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/asian-factories-remain-under-pressure-as-demand-rebound-eludes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 01:23:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>霍克斯比表示，新西兰联储不能忽视移民激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/rbnz-can-t-afford-to-ignore-surging-immigration-hawkesby-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行副行长克里斯蒂安·霍克斯比表示，新西兰央行不能忽视移民激增，尽管移民潮预计明年将会消退，因为通胀长期以来一直高于目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-01/rbnz-can-t-afford-to-ignore-surging-immigration-hawkesby-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2023 00:18:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
