    <item>
      <title>如果巴拿马关闭重要铜矿，第一量子将面临违反契约和成本削减的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/first-quantum-risks-covenant-breach-cost-cuts-if-panama-shuts-copper-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果巴拿马继续执行关闭一座去年利润约 10 亿美元的铜矿的计划，第一量子矿业有限公司 (First Quantum Minerals Ltd.) 明年可能会被迫放慢支出，并可能面临违反债务契约的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-29/first-quantum-risks-covenant-breach-cost-cuts-if-panama-shuts-copper-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 21:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行因持有债券而造成的账面损失创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-28/boj-s-paper-loss-on-bond-holdings-balloons-to-record-71-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行在最近六个月内创下了有记录以来最大的债券持有量未实现损失，这表明行长上田一夫如果走向政策正常化将面临挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-28/boj-s-paper-loss-on-bond-holdings-balloons-to-record-71-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 09:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
